<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/public-sector-fraud-authority> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Public Sector Fraud Authority works with departments and public bodies to understand and reduce the impact of fraud. PSFA is part of the Cabinet Office and HM Treasury ."@en .
